abstract: Autopsy of Sandra Bland, who died in jail cell three days after being arrested in traffic stop in Texas, rules death was suicide; finds numerous partially healed wounds on body.
lead_paragraph: The report showed that Ms. Bland, who was found dead in a Texas jail cell on July 13, tied a trash bag into a knot before using it as a ligature on her neck.

headline.main: Sandra Bland’s Autopsy Details How She Died
headline.print_headline: National Briefing | Southwest; Texas: Autopsy Released in Sandra Bland Death
